                            <comment id="66889" author="niu" created="Wed, 18 Sep 2013 02:33:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The log shows quota_ctl command to MDT failed with -3 (-ESRCH), which means quota on MDT isn&apos;t enabled properly, I think that&apos;s why MDT can&apos;t acquire quota from quota master and result in -EDQUOT at the end.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you check if there is any error message on MDS? and if possible, could you enable D_QUOTA &amp;amp; D_TRACE on MDS and collect log when running your test? (or lfs quota). Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="66862" author="mhanafi" created="Tue, 17 Sep 2013 19:40:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Got some additional debug info. Ran rpctrace and quota debuging on the client and it looks like the failure is releated to this error on the client.&lt;/p&gt;

